desc: Returns: Date/Time that the appointment is to take place, or requested new start time.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Date/Time that the appointment is to take place, or requested new start time.

name: $end
desc: Returns: This may be either the same as the appointment request to confirm the details of the appointment, or alternately a new time to request a re-negotiation of the end time.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: This may be either the same as the appointment request to confirm the details of the appointment, or alternately a new time to request a re-negotiation of the end time.

desc: Role of participant in the appointment.

name: $actor
desc: Returns: A Person, Location/HealthcareService or Device that is participating in the appointment.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A Person, Location/HealthcareService or Device that is participating in the appointment.

name: $participantStatus
desc: Returns: Participation status of the participant. When the status is declined or tentative if the start/end times are different to the appointment, then these times should be interpreted as a requested time change. When the status is accepted, the times can either be the time of the appointment (as a confirmation of the time) or can be empty.
